+Unions&amp;rft.place=Farnborough&amp;rft.pages=139-140&amp;rft.pub=Gower&amp;rft.date=1980&amp;rft.isbn=0566021609&amp;rft.aulast=Marsh&amp;rft.aufirst=Arthur&amp;rft.au=Ryan%2C+Victoria&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANational+Association+of+Schoolmasters\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">A. Blum (ed.), Teacher Unions and Associations: A Comparative Study, (University of Illinois Press, 1969), p. 54.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-R._Seifert_1995_p.97-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-R._Seifert_1995_p.97_7-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-R._Seifert_1995_p.97_7-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">M. Ironside and R. Seifert, Industrial Relations in Schools, (London: Routledge 1995), p.97</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-ironside-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-ironside_8-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Mike Ironside and Roger Seifert, <i>Industrial Relations in Schools</i>, p.92</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-TES200511-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-TES200511_9-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Michael Shaw (20 May 2011). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tes.co.uk/article.aspx?storycode=6082657&amp;navcode=94\">\"100 years of unions\"</a>. <i>TES Magazine</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">21 May</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=TES+Magazine&amp;rft.atitle=100+years+of+unions&amp;rft.date=2011-05-20&amp;rft.au=Michael+Shaw&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tes.co.uk%2Farticle.aspx%3Fst